# Normalize all text files to LF on checkout, on every OS. Without this the
# Windows CI runner checks out CRLF line endings and prettier (which expects LF)
# fails the lint step with hundreds of "Delete CR" warnings. `text=auto` lets Git
# auto-detect which files are text vs binary.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch their bytes.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
